&lt;p&gt;We are looking for Health care Assistants to come and join the team based on the Ambulatory Emergency Care Unit based at Ealing Hospital. Our service aims to provide same day emergency care for those patients attending with undifferentiated medical conditions thereby reducing hospital admissions and reducing the pressure on the emergency department. We have recently moved into a new department and are in the process of expansion to accommodate surgical and frailty pathways.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit healthcare assistants to enhance our patients care and journey. You will need to work as part of a large multi-disciplinary team and be able to work in a fast paced environment. If you are interested in high standards of patient care, have good communication skills and are highly motivated then this could be the area for you. Venepuncture and Cannulation skills are an advantage but training will be given. In return we offer a supportive atmosphere and access to training opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
